Instance of MobSquare, a FourSquare clone with a Mafia theme (using Facebook's API). 

Requirements:
    - Registered Facebook application
    - running MongoDB
    - pymongo - http://api.mongodb.org/python/
    - tornado web - http://www.tornadoweb.org/documentation

1. Fill in config.py.template with your values and copy them to config.py. On your local machine, for the login to work, you will want to
    set your "site url" to localhost:8888.